The above features of my system, and additional details, will become better understood by referring to the following detailed description and the attached drawings.


BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF THE DRAWINGS


In the drawings, like reference numerals refer to like parts throughout the various views, and wherein:


FIG. 1 is a pictorial view of a cryogenic railcar having a pallet racking system constructed in accordance with my invention, and shows the forward end of the railcar cut away and the racking system inside;


FIG. 2 is a cross-sectional view of the car and racking system shown in FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a view like FIG. 2 and shows the racking system supporting loaded pallets;


FIG. 4 is a cross-sectional view cut through a portion of the length of the car, from the door toward one end; and


FIG. 5 is a cross sectional view like FIG. 4 but illustrates the loading of pallets in the car.
